Paper: hep-th/9902157

Date: 1999-02-23

Title: Generalized statistics in one dimension

Authors: Alexios P. Polychronakos

Comments: Les Houches 1998 Lectures; 54 pages, LaTeX

SystemsAn exposition of the different definitions and approaches to quantumstatistics is given, with emphasis in one-dimensional situations. Permutationstatistics, scattering statistics and exclusion statistics are analyzed. TheCalogero model, matrix model and spin chain models constitute specificrealizations.